Host your next celebration at HENRY'S where office happy hours become legends, staff parties spark promotions, & networking events forge empires.
HENRY offers Bar Service & Food options, as well as event enhancements & catering. While we don't offer full depot takeovers, we rope off and dedicate a semi-private area for your group.
Complete the form below or email
events@thebasinsanford.com
